
# Infrastructure Diagrams

## Overview
Depicts deployment environment, cloud resources, and orchestration.

- Dockerized microservices
- CI/CD pipelines
- Backup & Disaster Recovery integration
- Optional cloud deployment (AWS/GCP/Azure)

*Suggested visual diagram using Mermaid:*

```mermaid
graph LR
    DEV[Developer] --> GH[GitHub Repository]
    GH --> CI[CI/CD Pipeline]
    CI --> DOCKER[Docker Containers]
    DOCKER --> APP[Application Services]
    APP --> DB[Database]
    APP --> FE[Frontend]
    APP --> LOG[Centralized Logging]

---

### âœ… Outcome

- **Developers**: Understand system flow and module interactions instantly.  
- **Auditors**: Clear traceability of data flow, agents, and infrastructure.  
- **Stakeholders**: High-level architecture overview for compliance and operational review.  
- **Onboarding**: Reduces ramp-up time for new engineers and external auditors.
